      Create your free style profile to explore our full community, get personalised matches based on your unique taste, and start a conversation with the right jeweller for you.
    </p>
    <button
      type="button"
      class="bg-btnPrimary btn-after text-white text-base leading-5 py-2 md:ml-0 min-h-[56px] min-w-[194px] px-6 rounded-full font-figtree font-medium btn-cta"
